# Copy to `.env.test` (git-ignored) to enable the logged-in browser tests.
#
# Use DEDICATED TEST accounts — never your real club data — so the tests
# never read or change real club data. Create each in Supabase Dashboard
# (Authentication → Users → Add user), then approve/assign roles.
#
# TEST_EMAIL/TEST_PASSWORD: used by most tests (members, messaging,
# calendar, profile, dark mode). A coach or member account works.
# Existing e2e-bot user can be reused here.
#
# ADMIN_EMAIL/ADMIN_PASSWORD: used only by e2e/admin.spec.ts for
# club_owner-only routes (/admin, /admin/users, etc.). Must be a real
# club_owner in the `users` table with status='active'.
# Without these, admin tests auto-skip.

# Optional: point the tests at a deployed site instead of a local server.
# BASE_URL=https://ra-club-app-git-main-ra-club-s-projects.vercel.app

TEST_EMAIL=
TEST_PASSWORD=
ADMIN_EMAIL=
ADMIN_PASSWORD=
